lead_paragraph: CANTER--Sid, beloved husband of Jane, father of Barry and Michael, father-in-law of Juan Tamargo and father of the late Steven; beloved brother of Robert of California and the late Alvin and Howard. Services at Congregation B'nai Jacob, Jersey City, Wednesday, February 5th at 1pm. For information 866-473-3700.
